ungsmuster in der Geschichte einer »westlichen« Erinnerungskultur zu hinterfragen.  aRemembering the atom bomb in the field of tension between tourism and the disarmament movement, between technical euphoria and collective grief: This volume provides changing perspectives and invites readers to question a common interpretative pattern.  afunded by Stiftung zur Förderung japanisch-deutscher Wissenschafts- und Kulturbeziehungen (JaDe-Stiftung).  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAtomkrieg. 4aErinnerung. 4aErinnerungskultur. 4aGeschichte des 20. Jahrhunderts. 4aHiroshima. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aMuseum. 4aMuseumswissenschaft. 4aTourismus. 4aZweiter Weltkrieg. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aCultural History.  aCultural Studies.  aHiroshima.  aHistory of the 20th Century.  aMemory Culture.  aMemory.  aMuseology.  aMuseum.  aNuclear War.  aSecond World War.  aTourism.2 aStiftung zur Förderung japanisch-deutscher Wissenschafts- und Kulturbeziehungen (JaDe-Stiftung).efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2018z9783110603231oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839438015zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839438015423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839438015/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZ